---
title: Redaguoti maisto planą — sequence diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor KT as Keliautojas

  participant FPV as FoodPlanView<br/>«boundary»
  participant FPPV as FoodPlacePickerView<br/>«boundary»
  participant MEV as MenuEditorView<br/>«boundary»

  participant JC as JourneyController<br/>«control»
  participant UC as UserController<br/>«control»

  participant Trip as Trip<br/>«entity»
  participant FP as FoodPlan<br/>«entity»
  participant Menu as Menu<br/>«entity»

  participant DB as DB

  KT->>FPV: redaguoti maisto planą
  FPV->>JC: getFoodPlan(tripId)
  JC->>DB: query(FoodPlan by tripId)
  DB-->>JC: foodPlanData
  JC-->>FPV: showFoodPlan(foodPlanData)
  FPV-->>KT: rodyti planą

  KT->>FPV: pridėti maisto vietą
  FPV->>FPPV: openPicker()
  FPPV->>JC: getFoodPlaces(route, preferences)
  JC->>DB: query(FoodPlace by route, preferences)
  DB-->>JC: foodPlaces
  JC-->>FPPV: foodPlaces
  FPPV-->>KT: rodyti pasirinkimus
  KT->>FPPV: pasirinkti vietą
  FPPV->>JC: addFoodPlace(tripId, placeId)
  JC->>FP: addPlace(placeId)
  FP-->>JC: ok

  KT->>FPV: redaguoti meniu
  FPV->>MEV: open(menuId)
  MEV->>JC: updateMenu(menuChanges)
  JC->>Menu: applyChanges(menuChanges)
  Menu-->>JC: ok

  JC->>DB: save(foodPlan)
  DB-->>JC: saved
  JC-->>FPV: foodPlanUpdated
  FPV-->>KT: maisto planas atnaujintas
